<paragraph blockId="38.[151,1437,712,1999]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,322,928,955]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
A species of 
<taxonomicName authorityName=": Silvestri" authorityYear="1909" box="[477,608,929,955]" class="Chilopoda" family="Aphilodontidae" genus="Mecophilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Geophilomorpha" pageId="38" pageNumber="39" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[477,608,929,955]" italics="true" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">Mecophilus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
with: known body length in adults more than 
